      "blocks": {
        "p_1": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As the Americana inspired name suggests, PENCO is a company making pens. That is, it started with a single ballpoint pen. By now their nostalgic analog collections encompass stationery ranging from clips to clipboards, notebooks to console boxes and pencases to, well… pens.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_2": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Penco is a Hightide brand, and their attention to design can be seen throughout the entire Hightide range of casual everyday stationery.</p>"
          }
